In time we grew apart. They were religious and as I aged I became agnostic. Using the values they taught me I became left leaning while they watched Fox News.

However, when a gunman showed up to his church today and started shooting, the first thing he did was get my nieces and nephews to safety. The next thing he did was run right back inside to save whoever else he could find.

The gunman found my father, shot him, poured gasoline over his corpse and set him on fire. The only mercy being he was dead before the fire was lit. I know this because my sister was there as she had run back into the building with him to help. The gunman let her go after forcing her to swear she worshiped Jesus and not Joseph Smith three times.

Whatever shortcomings my father may have had in life, in the end, when it mattered, he was the man I remembered as a child. He laid down his life for the people around him.

Greater love hath no man than this. He lived up to his values as a Christian. He lived up to my dreams as a child who idolized his father. He lived up to the basic decency that seems so absent in this day and age. I couldn't be prouder of him.

I'll miss you, Dad.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jpRoxE1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrBlackJack]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Incredible skill</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8mPUXXw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wDp187w.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8mPUXXw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Huor]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Reverend David black of the first Presbyterian Church of Chicago maced in the face at a demonstration today.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/c4IARc8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fL1Maj0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/c4IARc8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AndersCalrissian]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>That'll learn 'em</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/g7Xb0X7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vzTiCis.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/g7Xb0X7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JasonM1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>That's different</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/06lyqAH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L2rwn7M.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/06lyqAH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DOcelot1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Quite.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9vtUPiF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6FrsgXc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9vtUPiF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Az663]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sunday scratchies</title><link>https://img